  "title": {
    "zh-TW": "檢視者角色能力",
    "en": "Viewer Role Capabilities"
  },
  "content": {
    "type": "factual",
    "format": "markdown",
    "body": {
      "zh-TW": "檢視者可以搜索、列出和獲取節點、追蹤走訪、對節點進行評分（votes_up / votes_down），以及使用對話式問答。他們不能創建、修改或刪除任何節點、邊或工作區設置，也不能提出更改建議。",
      "en": "Viewers can search, list, and get nodes, track traversals, rate nodes (votes_up / votes_down), and use conversational Q&A. They cannot create, modify, or delete any nodes, edges, or workspace settings, nor can they propose changes."
    }
